{"tw": {"2875610": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "赫雷斯的角鬥場 Ⅲ", "steam_appid": 2875610, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3709900, 3709910], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/743583ae6dfdb5a01b4d093a63cc4023.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/743583ae6dfdb5a01b4d093a63cc4023.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/743583ae6dfdb5a01b4d093a63cc4023.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/16db476f92c8f97fe31ab45e0c00c36b.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span>一個遠離人煙，僻靜的向陽谷地內居住著一支百年之前為了逃離戰亂而來到此地的狐人族。村長班羅有一位美麗的夫人，以及兩個青春漂亮的女兒。長女奧蕾蒂與次女梅蘭妮。某天，一群兇惡的人口販子攻入村裡，擄走了大量人口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >慘遭人口販子擄走的奧蕾蒂被賣到了王都赫雷斯最黑暗的街道，她的主人是號稱黑街帝王的奴隸主古洛斯，好色易怒，又殘虐無道，從不把奴隸的性命當成一回事。奧蕾蒂在這裡遇見了同為奴隸，已經失去希望，不再追求自由的珊塔，以及在地下角鬥場擁有精靈女帝美譽的艾洛芬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奧蕾蒂必須想辦法在古洛斯無窮無盡的壓榨下活下去，以及擺脫奴隸紋魔法的影響，並且試圖尋找幫手。為了再次與家人相聚，同時與幫手合作，努力從古洛斯的恐怖統治下逃離。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/7c3ddc2699418bd487a258c7e9c2ef1f.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/7c3ddc2699418bd487a258c7e9c2ef1f.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/7c3ddc2699418bd487a258c7e9c2ef1f.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/58ce6055e44c68e04ae2ae2c3b08f6f7.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span>傳統王道日系RPG，角鬥士世界觀的延續之作，玩家將扮演奴隸奧蕾蒂，在這暗潮湧動的王都黑街，尋找生存的意義。除了在非法的地下角鬥場出賽之外，奧蕾蒂還得到娼館、酒館等地方打工賺錢以滿足古洛斯的貪欲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將在一次次的戰鬥以及艾洛芬的訓練下，一步一步的成長，多樣化的技能搭配加上角色成長系統，累積實力將成為你擺脫古洛斯統治的關鍵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/2f9d2fa645469768bdf3c79eb592bfbc.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/2f9d2fa645469768bdf3c79eb592bfbc.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/2f9d2fa645469768bdf3c79eb592bfbc.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/9f2fd3f4b264583d4f5373df003c4399.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span>保持初衷，相信總有一天能與家人團聚?<br>抑或是沉淪於淫慾，徹底淪落為古洛斯的玩物? <br>多路線結局，想在黑街如何生存全由你自行決定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/6176341fa619a56d1fcbccf37371ee25.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/6176341fa619a56d1fcbccf37371ee25.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"vid