ssets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/743583ae6dfdb5a01b4d093a63cc4023.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/743583ae6dfdb5a01b4d093a63cc4023.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/743583ae6dfdb5a01b4d093a63cc4023.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/1591e55b72daf1628d3d8141fc257b25.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span>In a secluded, sunlit valley, a foxkin tribe settled a century ago to escape war. The village chief, Banro, lives with his beautiful wife and two daughters: the eldest, Oretti and the younger, Melanie. But one day, their quiet life was shattered when the slave traders invaded. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oretti, kidnapped by slave traders, finds herself sold to Gulos, a cruel and merciless ruler of Jerez's darkest district. In this dreary place, she meets Shanta, who has already lost her hope for freedom, and Ailofen, the legendary Elven Empress of the underground arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oretti will have to survive Gulos's endless oppression, free herself from the effects of the magical slave mark, and seek out allies. Only by uniting with them will she be able to escape her cruel captivity and reunite with her family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/7c3ddc2699418bd487a258c7e9c2ef1f.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/7c3ddc2699418bd487a258c7e9c2ef1f.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/7c3ddc2699418bd487a258c7e9c2ef1f.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/6583f4ea46b057c8d91e761f1abf9c1f.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span>A traditional Japanese RPG about fighting for freedom. Players take on the role of Oretti, a slave in the capital's Shadow District. She fights in the underground arena, works in a brothel and tavern. With Ailofen's guidance, she will grow, develop skills, and gain strength to challenge Gulos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/0337a0f698000518672c902c6cbabe98.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/0337a0f698000518672c902c6cbabe98.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/0337a0f698000518672c902c6cbabe98.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/115b356adfd4cf318182ea033e012a50.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you hold on to the hope of being reunited with your family?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or will you succumb to lust and become Gulos's pet forever?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With multiple endings, your fate in the Shadow District is determined only by the choices you make!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/6176341fa619a56d1fcbccf37371ee25.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/6176341fa619a56d1fcbccf37371ee25.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/6176341fa619a56d1fcbccf37371ee25.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/0784eef9e33ce03b7f0eaba8cc0b3bad.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rather than killing you, the monsters here prefer to humiliate you in all sorts of perverted ways during battle...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/34a7ed0eab6ecf8e297c930c8feaa019.poster.avif?t=1763059021\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/34a7ed0eab6ecf8e297c930c8feaa019.webm?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/34a7ed0eab6ecf8e297c930c8feaa019.mp4?t=1763059021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/104fb2ec5fd15f9624358b6b6629a16c.avif?t=1763059021\" width=620 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted 